“NeuroScent Weaver” – A wearable device that uses micro-fluidic channels and precisely calibrated ultrasonic vibrations to deliver custom-blended scent profiles to the user’s olfactory system, dynamically adjusting based on real-time biofeedback data (heart rate, brainwave patterns, subtle muscle movements) to *reconstruct* and enhance recalled memories. The shape-memory alloy fibers within the device subtly modulate airflow, creating micro-currents that carry the scent and influence the wearer's perception of the memory. It's like a tiny, personalized olfactory time machine!